entry.content: My hearing loss journey has improved significantly since wearing my @Eargo hearing aids! #ad #HearingLoss can happen at any age but, like myself, so many young adults overlook the signs because of the age old stigma that hearing loss isn’t a problem until we’re older! Let’s #ShatterTheMyth ! Hearing health, in all ages, is so important so please check in with yourselves and each other and get your hearing screened! Go to Eargo.com/stories to hear more stories and learn more! #EargoDifference
